nodes.text: Vanessa Lengies (born July 21, 1985) is a Canadian actress, dancer, and singer. She has appeared in several television series including American Dreams, Hawthorne, and Glee. She is the voice actor of Kordi Freemaker, one of the four main protagonists of LEGO Star Wars: The Freemaker Adventures. She also provided additional voices in Rogue One: A Star Wars Story.
